{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-91-right-triangles-with-integer-coordinates","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-1-to-100","demoType":null,"title":"Vežba br. 91: Za desnu nogu sa punom koordinacijom","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Tačke ${P}(x_1, y_1)$ i ${Q}(x_2, y_2)$ nalaze se na celobrojnim koordinatama i povezane su sa koordinatnim početkom, ${O}(0, 0)$, formirajući trougao ${\\Delta}OPQ$.</p>\n<img alt=\"grafikon prikazuje tačke P (x_1, y_1) i Q(x_2, y_2) na celobrojnim koordinatama povezane sa koordinatnim početkom O (0, 0)\" src=\"https://cdn-media-1.freecodecamp.org/project-euler/right-triangles-integer-coordinates-1.png\" style=\"background-color: white; padding: 10px; display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; margin-bottom: 1.2rem;\">\n<p>Postoji četrnaest trouglova, posebno sa pravim uglom, koji se mogu formirati kada je svaka koordinata između 0 i 2 uključivo; tj., $0 ≤ x_1, y_1, x_2, y_2 ≤ 2$.</p>\n<img alt=\"dijagram prikazuje 14 pravouglih trouglova koji se mogu formirati kada su sve koordinate između 0 i 2\" src=\"https://cdn-media-1.freecodecamp.org/project-euler/right-triangles-integer-coordinates-2.png\" style=\"background-color: white; padding: 10px; display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; margin-bottom: 1.2rem;\">\n<p>Ako $0 ≤ x_1, y_1, x_2, y_2 ≤ limit$, koliko trouglova se može formirati?</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f3c71000cf542c50feda","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":302208,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-91-right-triangles-with-integer-coordinates"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function rightTrianglesIntCoords(limit) {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\nrightTrianglesIntCoords(2);","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>rightTrianglesIntCoords(2)</code> treba da vrati broj.</p>","testString":"assert(typeof rightTrianglesIntCoords(2) === 'number');"},{"text":"<p><code>rightTrianglesIntCoords(2)</code> treba da vrati <code>14</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(rightTrianglesIntCoords(2), 14);"},{"text":"<p><code>rightTrianglesIntCoords(10)</code> inapaswa kurudisha <code>448</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(rightTrianglesIntCoords(10), 448);"},{"text":"<p><code>rightTrianglesIntCoords(25)</code> treba da vrati <code>3207</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(rightTrianglesIntCoords(25), 3207);"},{"text":"<p><code>rightTrianglesIntCoords(50)</code> bi trebalo da vrati <code>14234</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(rightTrianglesIntCoords(50), 14234);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/project-euler/#project-euler-problems-1-to-100","dashedName":"problem-91-right-triangles-with-integer-coordinates","certification":"project-euler","disableLoopProtectTests":true,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"project-euler","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"project-euler-problems-1-to-100","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-92-square-digit-chains","prevChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-90-cube-digit-pairs","id":"5900f3c71000cf542c50feda","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"function arrangedProbability(limit) {\n  // Based on https://www.mathblog.dk/project-euler-100-blue-discs-two-blue/\n  let blue = 15;\n  let discs = 21;\n\n  while (discs < limit) {\n    const nextBlue = 3 * blue + 2 * discs - 2;\n    const nextDiscs = 4 * blue + 3 * discs - 3;\n\n    blue = nextBlue;\n    discs = nextDiscs;\n  }\n  return blue;\n}","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-91-right-triangles-with-integer-coordinates"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}